{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852152190,"sessionID":"ses_286f8510dffe7Btj6SgyzgA8f7","part":{"id":"prt_d790960a7001jXtzKQhYiZSO7H","messageID":"msg_d79095884001jOonw1jfwSU505","sessionID":"ses_286f8510dffe7Btj6SgyzgA8f7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_968bf5fa804f4556a0522542","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021: CLI build 命令 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** cmd/cli\n6: - **Language:** Python\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: <!-- TODO: Define delta requirements in Given/When/Then format -->\n13: \n14: ## File changes\n15: \n16: <!-- TODO: List file changes with action and description -->\n\n(End of file - total 16 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021: CLI build 命令 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** cmd/cli\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n<!-- TODO: Define delta requirements in Given/When/Then format -->\n\n## File changes\n\n<!-- TODO: List file changes with action and description -->","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775852152177,"end":1775852152188}}}}
